Run this command in your terminal in the directory OpenShot was downloaded to verify the SHA256 checksum:
  echo "380ada548e0c13d87cab9c520a3eaabab2d907b24e9d9f9160f685a29f1c0003  OpenShot-v3.5.0-x86_64.dmg" | shasum -a 256 --check

You should get the following output:
  OpenShot-v3.5.0-x86_64.dmg: OK